snippet.title: SQUAWKY - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist SQUAWKY on Steam  https://store.steampowered.com/app/3516220/Squawky/

SQUAWKY is the new upcoming indie mascot horror game for PC, coming to Steam in 2025 .  This new indie game is developed by a team of 3 people (Spark Labs Gaming).
